{"id":17931,"date":"2022-12-31T04:19:14","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:19:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke-va-khung-gam.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:19:14","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:19:14","slug":"toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke-va-khung-gam-2","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke-va-khung-gam-2\/","title":{"rendered":"Toyota Innova th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c v\u1ec1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 khung g\u1ea7m"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p><span class=\"location-stamp\">Indonesia<\/span><br \/>\nM\u1eabu MPV thay \u0111\u1ed5i thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng g\u1ea7m b\u1ec7 m\u1edbi d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, trang b\u1ecb g\u00f3i an to\u00e0n Toyota Safety Sense 3.0, b\u00e1n ra 3 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Sau nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 t\u1eebng ph\u1ea7n, k\u00e8m theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin nh\u1ecf gi\u1ecdt, Innova th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i Indonesia c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt gi\u1edd.  Xe s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u t\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.  Innova 2023 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n ra v\u1edbi 3 b\u1ea3n trang b\u1ecb g\u1ed3m G, V v\u00e0 Q c\u00f9ng t\u00f9y ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 x\u0103ng ho\u1eb7c hybrid.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Innova Zenix (\u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean t\u1ea1i Indonesia) hay HyCross (\u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean t\u1ea1i \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m m\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u xe v\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t 6 c\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u00e8n pha s\u1eafc n\u00e9t v\u00e0 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh h\u01a1n, h\u1ed1c h\u00fat gi\u00f3 cao h\u01a1n v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 g\u1ea7m.  C\u00e1ch s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp n\u00e0y kh\u00e1 gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e0n em Veloz.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u0110\u00e8n pha LED m\u1edbi, c\u1ea3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc g\u00e2n gu\u1ed1c h\u01a1n th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u0169.  Nh\u00ecn chung, Innova m\u1edbi tr\u00f4ng h\u1ea7m h\u1ed1 h\u01a1n, ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu nh\u1edd phong c\u00e1ch SUV.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Innova th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi v\u1eeba ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i Indonesia.  \u1ea2nh: Detikcom\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke.jpg\" title=\"toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke-300x195.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke-600x389.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Innova th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi v\u1eeba ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i Indonesia.  \u1ea2nh: Detikcom<\/p>\n<p>  <img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441804_12_toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"Innova m\u1edbi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00e8n pha LED, v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n cao c\u1ea5p c\u00f3 \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb ban ng\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e8n s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.\" title=\"1672441804_12_toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441805_754_toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"C\u1ed1p sau \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1edf b\u1eb1ng gi\u1ecdng n\u00f3i tr\u00ean c\u00e1c b\u1ea3n cao c\u1ea5p.\" title=\"1672441805_754_toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441805_208_toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"C\u1ee5m \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n trung t\u00e2m li\u1ec1n m\u1ea1ch v\u1edbi m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh th\u00f4ng tin gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed, v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u0169.\" title=\"1672441805_208_toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441805_283_toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"\u0110\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1.\" title=\"1672441805_283_toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441805_908_toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"C\u1eeda s\u1ed5 tr\u1eddi to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh tr\u00ean c\u00e1c b\u1ea3n cao c\u1ea5p.\" title=\"1672441805_908_toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441805_426_toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed cho h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf b\u1ea3n cao c\u1ea5p.\" title=\"1672441805_426_toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441805_961_toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"B\u1ea3n cao c\u1ea5p c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u1ec7 t\u00ec ch\u00e2n cho h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf th\u1ee9 hai.\" title=\"1672441805_961_toyota-innova-the-he-moi-lot-xac-ve-thiet-ke\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a Innova m\u1edbi v\u1edbi d\u00e0i x r\u1ed9ng x cao l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 4.755 x 1.850 x 1.795 mm.  \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i v\u00e0 r\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1u t\u0103ng th\u00eam 20 mm so v\u1edbi th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u0169.  Chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i c\u01a1 s\u1edf c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng th\u00eam 100 mm, \u0111\u1ea1t 2.850 mm so v\u1edbi 2.750 mm c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u0169.  Kho\u1ea3ng s\u00e1ng g\u1ea7m xe l\u00e0 185 mm, t\u0103ng 7 mm.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Trong cabin, b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i h\u01a1n, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa m\u1eb7t ph\u1eb3ng ngang v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ee9ng, kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.  B\u1ea3ng t\u00e1p-l\u00f4 c\u00f3 hai t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u gi\u1eefa n\u1eeda tr\u00ean v\u00e0 n\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi.  C\u1ee5m \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1, v\u00f4-l\u0103ng 3 ch\u1ea5u t\u00edch h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c ph\u00edm ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n trung t\u00e2m gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean cao h\u01a1n, n\u1eb1m trong m\u1ed9t thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 li\u1ec1n m\u1ea1ch v\u1edbi m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh trung t\u00e2m c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c h\u1ed1c gi\u00f3 h\u00ecnh ch\u1eef nh\u1eadt vi\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c.  M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh th\u00f4ng tin gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed 10 inch k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng minh tr\u00ean hai phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n cao c\u1ea5p V v\u00e0 Q. C\u00e1c n\u00fat b\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed ngay b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1eeda gi\u00f3 trung t\u00e2m.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Tr\u00ean hai phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n cao c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Innova 2023 l\u00e0 c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 tr\u1eddi to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh k\u00e9o d\u00e0i t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf th\u1ee9 3, gh\u1ebf ng\u1ed3i b\u1ecdc da hai t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft m\u1ea1 cr\u00f4m \u1edf \u1ed1p c\u1eeda.  M\u00e2m xe h\u1ee3p kim 18 inch tr\u00ean b\u1ea3n Q cao c\u1ea5p, trong khi b\u1ea3n V l\u00e0 17 inch v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n G d\u00f9ng v\u00e0nh 16 inch.  Hai phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n cao c\u1ea5p c\u00f2n c\u00f3 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed 10 inch cho h\u00e0nh kh\u00e1ch \u1edf h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf th\u1ee9 hai.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">M\u1eabu MPV th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng TNGA (GA-C) d\u1ea1ng li\u1ec1n th\u00e2n thay cho k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u khung b\u1eadc thang r\u1eddi nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.  D\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc thay v\u00ec d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea7u sau.  Phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n hybrid m\u1edbi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 x\u0103ng 2.0 v\u00e0 m\u00f4-t\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec7n v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 pin.  H\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 E-CVT.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u0110\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 x\u0103ng 2.0 v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VVT-i cho c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 171 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i 6.600 v\u00f2ng\/ph\u00fat v\u00e0 m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i 204 Nm.  Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n hybrid v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 2.0 cho c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t v\u00e0 m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn 149 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c.  \u2013 M\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn 187 Nm, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec7n 111 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn 205 Nm cho t\u1ed5ng c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 183 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb phanh tay \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1eef phanh t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng.  B\u1ea3n cao c\u1ea5p c\u00f3 c\u1eeda gi\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a tr\u00ean tr\u1ea7n xe, \u0111\u00e8n vi\u1ec1n n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, c\u1ed1p sau ch\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec7n, camera 360.  Innova 2023 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 2 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 EV v\u00e0 Eco &amp; Power.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">M\u1eabu MPV \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb g\u00f3i an to\u00e0n Toyota Safety Sense 3.0 v\u1edbi h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1eef l\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh th\u00edch \u1ee9ng.  H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng phanh \u0111\u0129a tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 4 b\u00e1nh t\u00edch h\u1ee3p phanh ABS v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n b\u1ed5 l\u1ef1c phanh \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">T\u1ea1i Indonesia, Innova Zenix b\u00e1n ra c\u00e1c phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n g\u1ed3m G AT m\u00e1y x\u0103ng, G AT HV (hybrid), V AT m\u00e1y x\u0103ng, V AT HV v\u00e0 Q HV.  Gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n 26.400-39.800 USD t\u00f9y phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\">M\u1ef9 Anh (theo Detikcom)<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Indonesia M\u1eabu MPV thay \u0111\u1ed5i thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng g\u1ea7m b\u1ec7 m\u1edbi d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, trang b\u1ecb g\u00f3i an to\u00e0n Toyota Safety Sense 3.0, b\u00e1n ra 3 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n. Sau nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 t\u1eebng ph\u1ea7n, k\u00e8m theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin nh\u1ecf gi\u1ecdt, Innova th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i Indonesia c\u00e1ch [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":16172,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17931"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=17931"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17931\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/16172"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=17931"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=17931"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=17931"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}